HEADWORD: forecasting
<hw>fore"cast*ing</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>The process of calculating and
predicting future events, usually based on extrapolation from past
experience, and with varying degress of uncertainty.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> prediction, foretelling.</syn>⟦br⟧
